  "body": "### Description\n\nIn the context [Regenerating project files](https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/discussions/41352) we would like to be able to regenerate docker files from the CLI.\r\n\r\nFor now we shall focus on\r\n- jvm\r\n- native\r\n- native-micro\r\n\r\nFor all of the above flavors we should have a simple build item that defines the from image.\r\n\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\nThis should most probably live inside an spi module of a new extension say `dockerfiles` like the spi module we have for kubernetes.",
